{"tid":2123244,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"選舉事務處一名常務助理確診","createTime":"2020-07-24T13:24:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T01:59:19.000Z","uid":5195,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9f42586d473d5768b18f86e89d9fba06346517f5","tid":2123244,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:24:31.000Z","msg":"選舉事務處證實，一名女常務助理確診新型冠狀病毒。處方指患者因家人是確診者，到醫院檢測後發現確診，目前已入院接受治療。她在九龍灣國際展貿中心十三樓工作，昨日最後一次上班，負責選民登記申請的後勤工作，辦公室並不對外開放，工作期間一直有戴口罩，體溫正常。處方指已安排全面清潔消毒工作地點，包括所有公用設施。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2348843\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2348843&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxS9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=0eda10f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2348843</a>"},{"pid":"473afde96419faeb4423e0cc1790e8fd72955ab5","tid":2123244,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:26:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">武漢肺炎</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b82515870d5104f4cf08aa906ddd6837f652625b","tid":2123244,"uid":199957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T14:36:31.000Z","msg":"大條道理推遲選舉"},{"pid":"bfa63ea767c79e5b4672449d5f274c031e2ddbdb","tid":2123244,"uid":271171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T14:38:38.000Z","msg":"劇本準備好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0edb34a5d6ef108d4cf1f54667cc01aad92df13","tid":2123244,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T01:59:19.000Z","msg":"延期了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}